CCPP-Awesome-M
===

联合循环机组性能计算程序包  
Combine Cycle Power Plant Performace Calculate Package

---

利用Python语言实现对燃气轮机、蒸汽轮机、余热锅炉经济性指标计算。  
Calculation of economic indexes of gas turbine, steam turbine, waste heat boiler using Python language.
